Usage: loadDrc [-help] <fileName> [-incremental]
               [-orient {r0 r90 r180 r270 mx mx90 my my90}] [-origin <x> <y>]

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
<fileName>            # fileName (string, required)
-incremental          # incremental (bool, optional)
-orient {r0 r90 r180 r270 mx mx90 my my90}
                      # Rotate all drcs in the file with the orientation (enum, optional)
-origin <x> <y>       # The origin coordinate of the drcs (point, optional)